            <span class="font-semibold">Enter Job Details</span>
            <p>Specify the job title, industry, and any additional relevant information about the open position.</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Select Experience Level and Interview Type</span>
            <p>Choose the candidate experience level and the types of questions you need (technical, behavioral, situational, etc.).</p>
          </li>
          <li class="text-lg">
            <span class="font-semibold">Add Optional Specific Skills and Company Values</span>
            <p>Include specific technical skills or company values to generate tailored questions that assess both competencies and cultural fit.</p>
          </li>
